Newsletter on Serial Transnational Nomination for World Heritage of Silk Roads.
The Newsletter on Serial Transnational Nomination for World Heritage of Silk Roads. Including headline news,Subjects,Progress report,Open platform of Information for Serial Transnational Nomination for World heritage of Silk Roads;And ICOMOS International Conservation Center work briefing. Preface from: Mr. Kishore Rao(Director of UNESCO World Heritage Centre) Mr. Tong Mingkang(Deputy Director of China State Administration of Cultural Heritage) Mr. Guo Zhan(Vice-President of ICOMOS) Supported by China State Administration of Cultural heritage(SACH) And UNESCO World Heritage Centre.
